CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, page 18, reads: "8. The Frigidaire dealers' booth was made enormous through the combination of Braddock Motor Supply Company, Modern Home Supply Company and Gaymar Company. Jack Quinn of Braddock Motor Supply Company is shown here"
TitMainTitle: Jack Quinn standing in a combination Braddock Motor Supply Company, Modern Home Supply Company, and Gaymar Company booth with Frigidaire appliances, in the Syria Mosque for the Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
